node.text:
Listen to the genuine care and respect CEO George Hill has built into the Diversified Chemical Technologies family. He also works to put black leaders in the best position to succeed by developing comprehensive succession plans to ensure his people experience generational growth. 

Throughout August, we’re celebrating #BlackBusinessMonth by sharing stories from our Black-owned suppliers to showcase how they’re cultivating more creativity, the best ideas, and innovative solutions by uplifting and supporting diverse communities.

shortcode_media.title: P&G | Black Business Month: Diversified Chemical Technologies
